Input template:  
example use {# template "admin/components/form/input" (arr "arg1" "arg2" "arg3" "arg4" "arg5") #}  
arg1 - id name  
arg2 - type input  
arg3 - rules for validation  
arg4 - span name  
arg5 - icon name  


Button template:  
example use {# template "admin/components/form/button" (arr "arg1" "arg2" "arg3" "arg4"%> #} 
arg1 - type input  
arg2 - span name  
arg3 - icon name  
arg4 - function name  
